ğŸ› ï¸ Getting Started
1. Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/no-code-email-filter-app.git
2. Set Up Google Sheets

Create sheets for Blocked Senders, Filter Rules, Log, Settings

3. Connect Google Sheets to AppSheet

Import the sheet

Configure views (Forms, Tables, Dashboards)

4. Build Automation

In Make, create a scenario with:

Gmail Watch Messages

Search sender in Blocked Senders sheet

If match â†’ Delete or Archive

Log action in Google Sheet

5. Deploy the App

Turn off or on sign-in depending on your needs

Get the public link from AppSheet â†’ Users > Links

